UID:IIGupVWIcyBmH3Bd3-rjX
SUMMARY:2026 March Chamber Mixer and Small Business Resource Fair
DTSTAMP:20260322T034733Z
DTSTART:20260325T223000Z
DESCRIPTION:Chamber Mixer - March \\+ Small Business Resource Fair Join us 
	for our March Chamber Mixer bringing together local professionals\, entrep
	reneurs\, and community leaders for an evening of connection\, collaborati
	on\, and valuable business resources. This month's mixer features a Small 
	Business Resource Fair\, where attendees can meet representatives from org
	anizations offering tools\, programs\, and guidance to help small business
	es grow and thrive. Whether you're looking to expand your network\, explor
	e partnership opportunities\, or learn about business support services\, t
	his event provides a welcoming environment to make meaningful connections.
	 Enjoy light refreshments\, engage with fellow professionals\, and discove
	r new resources to support your business journey-all while taking in insig
	hts from the Port of Seattle about upcoming initiatives that impact our re
	gional economy. Perfect for: ✔ Small business owners ✔ Startups and entrep
	reneurs ✔ Professionals looking to network ✔ Anyone interested in local bu
	siness resources We look forward to seeing you there!  BUSINESS INVOLVEMEN
	T OPPORTUNITIES: Sponsorship opportunities are still available\, for more 
	information please download our Seattle Southside Chamber Event Sponsorshi
	p Form.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/2026-march-chambe
	r-mixer-and-small-business-resource-fair/17995379/2026-03-25T00\n\nFrom SE
	Atoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/2026-march-chamber-mixer-
	and-small-business-resource-fair/17995379/2026-03-25T00
LOCATION:DoubleTree Hotel\, SeaTac\, 18740 International Blvd\, Seattle\, W
	A
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H30M
END:VEVENT
